data.description: BUYER INCENTIVE - $10,000 towards closing costs, rate buy down, etc. with acceptable offer! Welcome home! This home features an open floor plan, a fenced yard, 3 bedrooms PLUS a large bonus room (all you need is a door to make it a fourth bedroom)! The livingroom has a beautiful brick fireplace. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and the cutest bay window seat. Located close to groceries, local restaurants, shopping - only 30 minutes from Tybee Island and 15 minutes from Downtown Savannah! Don't miss your chance to be the new owner, come see it today!
